    "body": "@saradotramli Thanks for raising this.`truffle-contract` supports targeting a specific network at the 'class' level - e.g. you set the network of the contract abstraction and any instances created from it are on the named network. The API is [here](https://github.com/trufflesuite/truffle-contract#api). Does that seem like it would work for your use-case? \r\n\r\n\r\n",
